  Do it with style!<br>
  Body tag formatting attributes<br>
  link, vlink, bgcolor, background, style.<br>
  Style attribute can override your formatting concerns.<br>
  &lt;h1 style=&quot;color: red; font-style: italic&quot;&gt;</b></li>
  <li><b>  &quot;NO COMMENT! NO COMMENT&quot;<br>
  &lt;!-- Please make it a habit, to comment your pages--&gt;<br>
